rred tech stack if you have one?#{6}":[65,65],"#Round 1 Questions#Since you'll be building this with AI assistance, what is your preferred tech stack if you have one?#{7}":[66,67],"#Round 1 Questions#Since you'll be building this with AI assistance, what is your preferred tech stack if you have one?#Is this strictly a desktop web app, or is optimized mobile viewing a priority for quick logging?":[68,72],"#Round 1 Questions#Since you'll be building this with AI assistance, what is your preferred tech stack if you have one?#Is this strictly a desktop web app, or is optimized mobile viewing a priority for quick logging?#{1}":[70,71],"#Round 1 Questions#Since you'll be building this with AI assistance, what is your preferred tech stack if you have one?#Is this strictly a desktop web app, or is optimized mobile viewing a priority for quick logging?#{2}":[72,72],"#Round 2 Questions":[73,84],"#Round 2 Questions#1. The UX & Animation Flow (The \"Nothing OS\" Vibe)":[75,84],"#Round 2 Questions#1. The UX & Animation Flow (The \"Nothing OS\" Vibe)#**The Infinite Scroll Concept:** You mentioned wanting the entire app to feel like one continuous webpage with structural motion and instant navigation animations (likely using a tool like _Framer Motion_).":[77,81],"#Round 2 Questions#1. The UX & Animation Flow (The \"Nothing OS\" Vibe)#**The Infinite Scroll Concept:** You mentioned wanting the entire app to feel like one continuous webpage with structural motion and instant navigation animations (likely using a tool like _Framer Motion_).#{1}":[78,79],"#Round 2 Questions#1. The UX & Animation Flow (The \"Nothing OS\" Vibe)#**The Infinite Scroll Concept:** You mentioned wanting the entire app to feel like one continuous webpage with structural motion and instant navigation animations (likely using a tool like _Framer Motion_).#{2}":[80,81],"#Round 2 Questions#1. The UX & Animation Flow (The \"Nothing OS\" Vibe)#**The \"Health Snapshot\":** For the immediate dashboard view, you want a holistic picture of financial trajectory. If you had to pick the **one main hero metric** at the absolute top of the page, would it be **Net Worth** (past/present) or **Remaining Discretionary Budget** (the day-to-day focus)?":[82,84],"#Round 2 Questions#1. The UX & Animation Flow (The \"Nothing OS\" Vibe)#**The \"Health Snapshot\":** For the immediate dashboard view, you want a holistic picture of financial trajectory. If you had to pick the **one main hero metric** at the absolute top of the page, would it be **Net Worth** (past/present) or **Remaining Discretionary Budget** (the day-to-day focus)?#{1}":[84,84]},"outlinks":[],"metadata":{"tags":["#Project","#finance","#projects/fin-app/project-doc"]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},"smart_blocks:01_Projects/fin-app/System requirements - Brainstorm.md#Round 2 Questions": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"gqff59","at":1780746289700},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06759954,-0.06134607,0.01025193,-0.05950462,-0.09325486,0.06158416,-0.05860657,0.01249304,0.03296135,0.024848,0.01909759,0.07809627,0.03527917,0.07632059,0.0086977,-0.01035494,0.03927026,-0.00266478,-0.03249418,0.08771921,0.04534119,-0.02220738,0.00325015,-0.02028954,0.02693014,0.02852294,-0.03258341,-0.07301819,0.01078474,-0.20094641,-0.01735775,-0.02629163,-0.03030027,-0.03449857,-0.02554216,0.01306155,-0.03183429,0.06859121,-0.0096328,0.03526161,0.01223031,0.09969945,-0.02063386,-0.01775977,0.06911147,-0.07860057,0.01251549,0.0274065,-0.02224711,0.07151683,-0.00833357,-0.05204314,0.04404666,-0.01361659,-0.01292402,0.04535329,-0.00109848,0.03195795,0.02941874,0.01802326,0.05915479,-0.02100354,-0.14648555,0.12106746,0.04965559,0.03941251,-0.04091041,0.00317711,0.04542167,0.05308707,-0.01267678,0.00766236,-0.01050455,0.05204265,0.04016459,-0.06217498,0.07131407,-0.01716837,0.01785151,-0.00783463,0.004115,-0.01326181,-0.03141782,-0.05203347,0.01011679,0.05422372,0.02007205,-0.05431104,0.0103526,0.00540604,-0.0101138,-0.