 (The \"What\")#How do you want the financial data to get into the app?":[27,32],"#Round 1 Questions#2. Features and Functionality (The \"What\")#How do you want the financial data to get into the app?#{1}":[29,29],"#Round 1 Questions#2. Features and Functionality (The \"What\")#How do you want the financial data to get into the app?#{2}":[30,30],"#Round 1 Questions#2. Features and Functionality (The \"What\")#How do you want the financial data to get into the app?#{3}":[31,32],"#Round 1 Questions#2. Features and Functionality (The \"What\")#What are the absolute \"must-have\" features for Version 1 (MVP)?":[33,42],"#Round 1 Questions#2. Features and Functionality (The \"What\")#What are the absolute \"must-have\" features for Version 1 (MVP)?#{1}":[35,35],"#Round 1 Questions#2. Features and Functionality (The \"What\")#What are the absolute \"must-have\" features for Version 1 (MVP)?#{2}":[36,36],"#Round 1 Questions#2. Features and Functionality (The \"What\")#What are the absolute \"must-have\" features for Version 1 (MVP)?#{3}":[37,37],"#Round 1 Questions#2. Features and Functionality (The \"What\")#What are the absolute \"must-have\" features for Version 1 (MVP)?#{4}":[38,38],"#Round 1 Questions#2. Features and Functionality (The \"What\")#What are the absolute \"must-have\" features for Version 1 (MVP)?#{5}":[39,39],"#Round 1 Questions#2. Features and Functionality (The \"What\")#What are the absolute \"must-have\" features for Version 1 (MVP)?#{6}":[40,41],"#Round 1 Questions#2. Features and Functionality (The \"What\")#What are the absolute \"must-have\" features for Version 1 (MVP)?#{7}":[42,42],"#Round 1 Questions#3. User Experience & Design (The \"How it feels\")":[43,44],"#Round 1 Questions#When you open the app, what is the very first piece of information you want to see on your dashboard?":[45,55],"#Round 1 Questions#When you open the app, what is the very first piece of information you want to see on your dashboard?#{1}":[47,47],"#Round 1 Questions#When you open the app, what is the very first piece of information you want to see on your dashboard?#{2}":[48,48],"#Round 1 Questions#When you open the app, what is the very first piece of information you want to see on your dashboard?#{3}":[49,50],"#Round 1 Questions#When you open the app, what is the very first piece of information you want to see on your dashboard?#Are there any existing finance apps, websites, or spreadsheets you’ve used that you liked or disliked? What stood out about them?":[51,55],"#Round 1 Questions#When you open the app, what is the very first piece of information you want to see on your dashboard?#Are there any existing finance apps, websites, or spreadsheets you’ve used that you liked or disliked? What stood out about them?#{1}":[53,54],"#Round 1 Questions#When you open the app, what is the very first piece of information you want to see on your dashboard?#Are there any existing finance apps, websites, or spreadsheets you’ve used that you liked or disliked? What stood out about them?#{2}":[55,55],"#Round 1 Questions#4. Tech & Scope (The \"Under the hood\")":[56,57],"#Round 1 Questions#Since you'll be building this with AI assistance, what is your preferred tech stack if you have one?":[58,72],"#Round 1 Questions#Since you'll be building this with AI assistance, what is your preferred tech stack if you have one?#{1}":[60,60],"#Round 1 Questions#Since you'll be building this with AI assistance, what is your preferred tech stack if you have one?#{2}":[61,61],"#Round 1 Questions#Since you'll be building this with AI assistance, what is your preferred tech stack if you have one?#{3}":[62,62],"#Round 1 Questions#Since you'll be building this with AI assistance, what is your preferred tech stack if you have one?#{4}":[63,63],"#Round 1 Questions#Since you'll be building this with AI assistance, what is your preferred tech stack if you have one?#{5}":[64,64],"#Round 1 Questions#Since you'll be building this with AI assistance, what is your preferred tech stack if you have one?#{6}":[65,65],"#Round 1 Questions#Since you'll be building this with AI assistance, what is your preferred tech stack if you have one?#{7}":[66,67],"#Round 1 Questions#Since you'll be building this with AI assistance, what is your preferred tech stack if you have one?#Is this strictly a desktop web app, or is optimized mobile viewing a priority for quick logging?":[68,72],"#Round 1 Questions#Since you'll be building this with AI assistance, what is your preferred tech stack if you have one?#Is this strictly a desktop web app, or is optimized mobile viewing a priority for quick logging?#{1}":[70,71],"#Round 1 Questions#Since you'll be building this with AI assistance, what is your preferred tech stack if you have one?#Is this strictly a desktop web app, or is optimized mobile viewing a priority for quick logging?#{2}":[72,72],"#Round 2 Questions":[73,97],"#Round 2 Questions#1. The UX & Animation Flow (The \"Nothing OS\" Vibe)":[75,85],"#Round 2 Questions#1. The UX & Animation Flow (The \"Nothing OS\" Vibe)#**The Infinite Scroll Concept:** You mentioned wanting the entire app to feel like one continuous webpage with structural motion and instant navigation animations (likely using a tool like _Framer Motion_).":[77,81],"#Round 2 Questions#1. The UX & Animation Flow (The \"Nothing OS\" Vibe)#**The Infinite Scroll Concept:** You mentioned wanting the entire app to feel like one continuous webpage with structural motion and instant navigation animations (likely using a tool like _Framer Motion_).#{1}":[78,79],"#Round 2 Questions#1. The UX & Animation Flow (The \"Nothing OS\" Vibe)#**The Infinite Scroll Concept:** You mentioned wanting the entire app to feel like one continuous webpage with structural motion and instant navigation animations (likely using a tool like _Framer Motion_).#{2}":[80,81],"#Round 2 Questions#1. The UX & Animation Flow (The \"Nothing OS\" Vibe)#**The \"Health Snapshot\":** For the immediate dashboard view, you want a holistic picture of financial trajectory. If you had to pick the **one main hero metric** at the absolute top of the page, would it be **Net Worth** (past/present) or **Remaining Discretionary Budget** (the day-to-day focus)?":[82,85],"#Round 2 Questions#1. The UX & Animation Flow (The \"Nothing OS\" Vibe)#**The \"Health Snapshot\":** For the immediate dashboard view, you want a holistic picture of financial trajectory. If you had to pick the **one main hero metric** at the absolute top of the page, would it be **Net Worth** (past/present) or **Remaining Discretionary Budget** (the day-to-day focus)?#{1}":[84,85],"#Round 2 Questions#2. **Data Ingestion & \"Diverse Archetypes\"**":[86,97],"#Round 2 Questions#2. **Data Ingestion & \"Diverse Archetypes\"**#**The Manual/CSV Process:** Since Australian open banking can be restrictive, CSV uploads are a smart MVP choice.":[88,92],"#Round 2 Questions#2. **Data Ingestion & \"Diverse Archetypes\"**#**The Manual/CSV Process:** Since Australian open banking can be restrictive, CSV uploads are a smart MVP choice.#{1}":[90,91],"#Round 2 Questions#2. **Data Ingestion & \"Diverse Archetypes\"**#**The Manual/CSV Process:** Since Australian open banking can be restrictive, CSV uploads are a smart MVP choice.#{2}":[92,92],"#Round 2 Questions#2. **Data Ingestion & \"Diverse Archetypes\"**#**Account Archetypes:** You want to track everything from neobanks to stocks and managed funds.":[93,97],"#Round 2 Questions#2. **Data Ingestion & \"Diverse Archetypes\"**#**Account Archetypes:** You want to track everything from neobanks to stocks and managed funds.#{1}":[95,96],"#Round 2 Questions#2. **Data Ingestion & \"Diverse Archetypes\"**#**Account Archetypes:** You want to track everything from neobanks to stocks and managed funds.#{2}":[97,97]},"outlinks":[],"metadata":{"tags":["#Project","#finance","#projects/fin-app/project-doc"]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},"smart_blocks:01_Projects/fin-app/System requirements - Brains